    "description": "StartFragmentThis collection provides a complete set of API requests to test a session-based authentication system. It covers user registration, login, session management, and protected user operations such as fetching and updating profile data. The collection is designed to validate authentication flows, ensure secure session handling, and demonstrate how authorized access is enforced within a Node.js and PostgreSQL backend in a local development environment.",
